snippet.title: Fighters Destiny Trailer 1998
snippet.description:
Fighters Destiny Trailer 1998

Official Content From Ocean

The best fighting game for 64. Awesome characters, cool moves, and 5 different fighting modes. Rodeo mode puts you in a small ring against a deadly cow (..yes cow..) to see how long you can live.
Platforms: Nintendo 64
